Titolo: LIT (video game)

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: LIT, known as School of Darkness (スクール オブ ダークネス, Sukūru obu Dākunesu) in Japan, is a video game by WayForward Technologies for WiiWare. The game is directed by Adam Tierney and co-designed by Tierney and Matt Bozon. It was released in North America on February 9, 2009.The game has been described as a "horror puzzler", and its style of gameplay has been compared to Sokoban, Chip's Challenge and the Adventures of Lolo series. It is built around the concept that "light is life and darkness is death".

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
